						that enables you to be specifically identified (e.g. by reference to your name or email address).
					</p>
					<p>
						<b>Facebook:</b> We also use the pixel function of Facebook Custom Audiences to identify users who have
						landed on certain pages for the purposes of target group-orientated remarketing and advertising.
						The Facebook pixel stores a cookie, which means that information about your visit to our Our Wave Partner Site
